    Delimits a section of 'raw' text.
    Not valid in ``@root`` or ``@unit`` trees.

\@root, \@root-code and \@root-code
    Start an ``@root`` tree.
    ``@root-code`` and ``root-doc`` specify whether body text starts in code or doc mode by default.

